ets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n轉眼間原來你係藍店系列又嚟啦💞💞<br />\n今次要講嘅主題係咖啡店 <br />\n<br />\n講起咖啡 <br />\n應該好多人第一時間諗起Starbucks同Pacific Coffee <br />\n但你又知唔知哩兩間連鎖咖啡店係邊個集團嘅旗下? <br />\n答案:Starbucks係由美心食品旗下 Pacific Coffee係華潤集團旗下🤯<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如果你地想知道埋其他藍店嘅背景 <br />\n可以swipe去圖七</span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n圖七上面簡短地列出14間藍店嘅背景資料同原因(字體較細 希望見諒🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️)<br />\n<br />\n另外大家有資料想補充或者有其他黃/藍店嘅資料(任何店鋪) <br />\n歡迎隨時報料 報料:<a href=\"http://t.me/suck_helper_bot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsuck_helper_bot&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZ0trSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=388fc0b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/suck_helper_bot</a><br />\n<br />\n大家睇完有咩意見 歡迎去我哋Instagram/Facebook留言👩🏻&zwj;💻<br />\n<br />\nIG : <a href=\"http://instagram.com/suckchannel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fsuckchannel&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZ0trSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=802e76c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">instagram.com/suckchannel</a> <br />\nFB : <a href=\"http://facebook.com/tgsuckchannel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Ftgsuckchannel&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZ0trSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=d72f7584\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">facebook.com/tgsuckchannel</a> <br />\n<br />\n我哋一定會繼續出更多高質嘅post畀你哋 密切留意我哋IG同FB🙂<br />\n<br />\n#2為黃店"},{"pid":"e99f5ac6b45fedf0c86e0c0c4b3cda5d03b8eb83","tid":1995492,"uid":282534,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T09:49:11.000Z","msg":"#2<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YdChiQQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYdChiQQ.jpg&h=6e14ab67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iab2uXA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fiab2uXA.jpg&h=2ce2a8e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3BE0gCJ.jpg\" data-thumbn