Oz5wq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FypOz5wq.jpg&h=8febd0c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uLhhiRA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuLhhiRA.jpg&h=4c6da812&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a9xQDRE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa9xQDRE.jpg&h=f57eca0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZBXhiRJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZBXhiRJ.jpg&h=643842de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q47pJiD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ47pJiD.jpg&h=6266f873&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">原來你係黃店[咖啡店篇]<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n第一件事 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">登記做選民</span></strong></span>!!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n*新登記選民可透過選舉事務處進行網上登記<br />\n<br />\n第二件事 今日開始係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">五一黃金週</span></strong></span>嘅第一日 記得要多啲支持黃店💛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n五一黃金IG@fivedemandsweek<br />\n<br />\n平時鐘意飲咖啡嘅朋友 <br />\n就一定要留意我呢一篇 <br />\n今次我列出咗二十間港九新界嘅cafe同coffee shop <br />\n除咗會有知名度比較高嘅咖啡店 <br />\n今次特登加入咗幾間細店 <br />\n希望多啲朋友可以支持下佢哋💛<br />\n<br />\n咁當然啦 <br />\n香港仲有好多好多好多間黃店咖啡店 <br />\n但空間有限 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔可以將所有咖啡加哂落去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果今個篇章反應好嘅話 <br />\n我會考慮出PART 2 繼續滿足你哋嘅需要<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果大家有其他黃店或藍店嘅資料(任何店鋪) 歡迎隨時報料 <br />\n報料:<a href=\"http://t.me/suck_helper_bot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsuck_helper_bot&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZ0trSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=388fc0b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/suck_helper_bot</a><br />\n<br />\n大家睇完有咩意見 歡迎去我哋Instagram/Facebook留言👩🏻&zwj;💻<br />\n<br />\nIG <a href=\"http://instagram.com/suckchannel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fsuckchannel&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZ0trSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=802e76c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">instagram.com/suckchannel</a> <br />\nFB <a href=\"http://facebook.com/tgsuckchannel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Ftgsuckchannel&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZ0trSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=d72f7584\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">facebook.com/tgsuckchannel</a> <br />\n<br />\n我哋一定會繼續出更多高質嘅post畀你哋 <br />\n密切留意我哋IG同FB🙂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T11:01:41.000Z","msg":"日日會自己係屋企手沖<br />\n咖啡公義ｄ咖啡豆好似好黃下<br />\n樓主知唔知飲左呢間個口會唔會變黃？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.coffee-justice.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.coffee-justice.com%2F&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZ0trSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=e2212899\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.coffee-justice.com/</a>"},{"pid":"76a0881ee13490650f077078a2d4d9d13e49b834","tid":1995492,"uid":86649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T13:09:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0a246450aef67151cefb11d75a3dbf79546a103","tid":1995492,"uid":220942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T13:38:12.000Z","msg":"&quot;原來你係黃店&quot;<br />\n應該變做<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&quot;好彩你係黃店&quot;</span></span>"},{"pid":"df996a59d3ce957ece804813f726ab1e1ad5c443","tid":1995492,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T13:45:35.000Z","msg":"第7果間藍店係咩集團<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f50b9e6b21227ce7ef710698140033b7bbb71960","tid":1995492,"uid":66357,"li